---
description: Python conventions (Vercel runtime aligned)
globs: ["src/**", "api/**", "tests/**", "pyproject.toml", "requirements*.txt"]
alwaysApply: true
---
- Target runtime: Python 3.11 (Vercel). Local tooling may use newer Python, but code must remain 3.11-compatible.
- Prefer stdlib first. Keep dependencies minimal.
- Secrets from env vars only (AIRTABLE_API_TOKEN, AIRTABLE_BASE_ID, API_KEY).
- HTTP clients must set timeouts; Airtable client must enforce 5 RPS and pagination.
- Logging must avoid PII; mask emails/phones.
